description:
Contents:
 - Bright Yellow Country Wear "A casual outfit designed to look like the clothes worn by an agricultural worker."
 - Bright Yellow Kid's Country "A casual outfit for kids designed to look like the clothes worn by an agricultural worker."
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop (Clothing Store in Castle St.) when you purchase it.
 - Flower Hat: Bright Yellow "A straw hat decorated with a colorful array of flowers."
 - Small Flower Hat: Yellow "A small straw hat decorated with a colorful array of flowers."
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop (Fashion Store in Castle St.) when you purchase it.
name: Bright Yellow Country Wear Set
